    "style": "Heading 1",
    "text": "1. Introduction to Volume 5"
  },
  {
    "style": "First Paragraph",
    "text": "Volume 5 of the DGOP v4.1 Master Specification defines the security architecture, regulatory compliance mappings, and audit framework for the Enterprise Data Governance Operations Platform. This volume translates the governance and operational requirements defined in Volumes 1-4 into concrete security controls, compliance evidence, and assurance mechanisms. It serves as the authoritative reference for security engineers, compliance officers, Data Protection Officers (DPO), and auditors responsible for certifying DGOP against KSA national standards."
  },
