    "style": "Heading 1",
    "text": "7. Audit & Logging Architecture"
  },
  {
    "style": "Heading 2",
    "text": "7.1 Audit Pipeline Architecture"
  },
  {
    "style": "Compact",
    "text": "Security Events: OPA decision logs (including ABAC attributes evaluated), Vault audit logs, Keycloak event logs, WAF alerts (ModSecurity), masking operation logs, PbD gate transitions, search query logs, error event logs, notification delivery logs, authentication failure logs, and SIEM correlation events aggregated via syslog-ng and Fluentd."
  },
  {
    "style": "Compact",
    "text": "Executive security dashboard (Grafana) displays: failed login attempts (last 24h), top 10 sensitive data access events, open DLP incidents, overdue security reviews, mTLS compliance percentage, ABAC decision latency, masking operation volume, search query volume and anomaly count, error rate by service, and notification delivery success rate."
  },
