    "text": "8. Security Operations & Incident Response"
  },
  {
    "style": "First Paragraph",
    "text": "Security operations (SecOps) encompass the people, processes, and technologies that maintain DGOP security posture on a continuous basis. This section defines incident response procedures, vulnerability management, penetration testing, security monitoring, and workflow engine security controls aligned with NCA ECC and PDPL breach notification requirements."
